data.description: Stunning Brick Colonial Home located in desirable Simmons Acres Community. Large 4,824 sq ft - with 4 Bedrooms & 3.5 Bathrooms.  The two-story Entry features a Beautiful Chandelier, Gleaming Hardwood Flooring and large Transom Window that lets the natural light pour in.  Entire House Freshly Painted and NEW Carpeting on Main Level, Staircase and Catwalk.  Traditional Floor Plan has Sitting Room & Dinning Room with floor to ceiling Windows.  Large 2 level family room with Vaulted Ceiling and wall of windows also features a Gas Fireplace.  Step right into the Oversized Kitchen with Island and Breakfast Nook leading to Deck, perfect for Cookouts and relaxing quiet evenings.  Kitchen has a perfect Island for Entertaining while preparing meals on the Island Cook Top and Double Wall Oven.  Lots of Kitchen Storage with the Walk In Pantry and tons of Cabinets allows you to Easily access everything you need.  Main Level also provides a large Office tucked off of the Living Room.  The  Upper Level's Primary Bedroom with a walk in closet and its own Bathroom with a garden soaking tub and separate shower.  There are 3 additional Spacious bedrooms.  Large Basement is amazing featuring a  Theater Room, Game Room / Bar, Work Out Room a 3rd Full Bathroom and Unfinished area for a workshop and extra storage space. 2 Car Garage and Plenty of Parking space in the driveway.  Enjoy the Community Amenities - Outdoor Pool, Tennis Courts & Tot Lots.  Close to Amazing Entertainment - National Golf Club, National Harbor, MGM, Tanger Outlets, many restaurants, shops and Marinas.  Easy commute to Andrews Joint Air Force Base, Arlington VA and Washington DC.
